<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Suspended</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #e0e0e0; padding: 32px; }
        h2 { color: #d32f2f; }
        p { color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
        .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Account Suspended</h2>
        <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
        <p>
            We regret to inform you that your account on <strong>Local Marketplace</strong> has been suspended due to a violation of our terms of service.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you believe this is a mistake or would like more information, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@localmarketplace.com">support@localmarketplace.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Thank you for your understanding.<br>
            <strong>The Local Marketplace Team</strong>
        </p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Local Marketplace. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>